# Add patterns of files dvc should ignore, which could improve
# the performance. Learn more at
# https://dvc.org/doc/user-guide/dvcignore
# 1. EXCLUDE all files and folders globally
*

# 2. UN-EXCLUDE (Re-include) the specific file types DVC should track
# The double asterisk (**) matches any directory depth.
!**/*.pkl
!**/*.json
!**/*.csv

# 3. UN-EXCLUDE necessary metadata files for DVC/Git
!.dvcignore
!dvc.yaml
!.gitignore